text.tspan: Icons are at least 2 units apart from each other
Leftmost event is 4 units from the fight
Skull is for random death via non-monster causes
Blood for... messy. Usually for dying in a fight.
Heartbreak is for death of parent during childbirth
Lantern is for participating and surviving a fight
Red monster lines for nemesis encounters
Wider lines (0.5, 0.75, 1 mm) for levels 1, 2, 3, respectively
